
Cucumber is a software tool that supports behavior-driven development

Advantages of Cucumber:
1. Supports languages like Java and Ruby
2. End-to-end test framework
3. Code re-usability
4. Easy to understand

TDD: TDD is focused on testing smaller pieces of functionality individually
- usually done only by developer
BDD: BDD is designed to test an application’s behavior from the end user’s standpoint
- done by team (devs, testers and managers)
